(8, 'contact', 'Sonakshi Goel', 'sonakshigoel73@gmail.com', '8826644980', 'Pune', 'To The Human Resources Department,\n\n I am so excited about the opportunity to apply for the Interior Designer position with your company. Throughout my life, I have pursued interior design with passion, and the skills I have acquired along the way make me an exceptional candidate for this job. I love putting my creativity to work to produce the best outcome for my clients regarding style and function. Thanks to my commitment to my art, I have secured a degree in interior designing and accomplished many projects. \n\nI have been honored to help design some of the most prolific interiors in town. I received various types of projects for my six weeks internship in the summer of 2019. It was my task to assist my senior designer and work under his guidance. In january 2020, I was offered a position of interior designer and extended my work profile in different sectors, connected with clients and contractors to achieve and execute the desired design. \n\nThe experiences during my work journey of 3 years were demanding challenges that helped me grow into an artist who knows the industry\'s ins and outs. I have learned that an artistic eye is one small part of being a good designer. Not only have I had the opportunity to hone my communication skills and creative problem solving, but I have also learned essential budgeting skills and time management. My flexibility and willingness to adapt made me resilient to hiccups and unforeseen circumstances. I am impressed with how your company puts customer satisfaction first and reaches for the highest attainable goal wherever possible. I hope to be a part of your mission to bring fashion and function to people seeking sophisticated style in their homes. Please feel free to reach out if you have any questions. \n\nI look forward to hearing from you. \n\nSincerely, \n\nSonakshi Goel  \nsonakshigoel73@gmail.com\n(+91)8826644980', NULL, NULL, '2024-02-0